# Financial Risk Determination Basis Code

## identifier
de13053

## type
string

## definition
The basis used for determination as at the relevant date.

## guidance
Valid values are:
Gross = The basis used to calculate the reported information was gross of reinsurance recoveries. 
Net = The basis used to calculate the reported information was net of reinsurance recoveries.

## codes
| Name  |
| ----- |
| Gross |
| Net   |

## syntax
### xbrl
- name=FinancialRisk.DeterminationBasis.Code
- classification=baf/bafot/bafot.02.12
- period=instant
